## Technical stack

- **Frontend**: Next.js (App Router), Tailwind CSS
- **Backend / DB**: Supabase (Postgres, Auth, Storage, Realtime)
- **Hosting**: Vercel
- **Repo**: github.com/patrickdelaney-alt/royalfitness
- **Platform**: iOS (App Store live), web TBD

---

## Success looks like

- Users opening Royal at the gym to track live workouts, not just to post about them after
- Logging feeling so fast that it becomes a habit without thinking
- Catalog referral links being used organically, not aggressively promoted
- Location discovery driving real-world wellness behaviour — trying a new gym, finding a sauna
- Word of mouth from people who describe Royal as "Strava but for everything wellness"
